Robot Class
=================
The Robot class in Java is part of the java.awt package. 
It is used to simulate native keyboard and mouse actions 
at the operating system level. 

In Selenium, the Robot class is helpful when Selenium 
cannot interact directly with certain OS-level components 
such as file upload dialogs or keyboard shortcuts.


